@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Message from the Leadership - ASBM";
}
<h2 class="page-title">📜 Message from the Leadership</h2>
<p class="sub-title">Words of Wisdom & Inspiration from Our Esteemed Leaders</p>

<div class="message-container">
    <div class="message-card">
        <h3>🎓 Message from the Chancellor</h3>
        <p>Welcome to Aditya School of Business Management! Our mission is to create a transformative educational experience that nurtures future leaders, innovators, and entrepreneurs. ASBM is committed to excellence in academics, research, and corporate partnerships.</p>
        <p>- Prof. Rajesh Sharma, Chancellor</p>
    </div>

    <div class="message-card">
        <h3>🏛️ Director's Vision</h3>
        <p>At ASBM, we foster a culture of learning, leadership, and creativity. Our institution stands as a bridge between knowledge and real-world application, ensuring that our students emerge as global professionals.</p>
        <p>- Dr. Neeta Verma, Director</p>
    </div>

    <div class="message-card">
        <h3>📘 Principal’s Message</h3>
        <p>Education is not just about acquiring knowledge; it is about developing skills, values, and vision. ASBM is dedicated to providing a world-class learning experience through innovation and industry-aligned programs.</p>
        <p>- Dr. Vikram Patil, Principal</p>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    /* Background Styling */
    body {
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #FFD700, #1E90FF);
        font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        color: black;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
    }

    .page-title {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 38px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-top: 20px;
        text-shadow: 3px 3px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .sub-title {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        font-weight: 500;
    }

    /* Message Cards */
    .message-container {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 20px;
        padding: 30px;
    }

    .message-card {
        background: white;
        padding: 25px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        text-align: center;
        width: 400px;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        position: relative;
    }

        .message-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
        }

        .message-card h3 {
            color: #1E90FF;
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .message-card p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

            .message-card p:last-child {
                font-weight: bold;
                margin-top: 15px;
                color: #0047AB;
            }
</style>
